QuestionCN:
在平面直角坐标系中,已知点A(0,a),B(0,b),C(7,-2),连接BC,(\sqrt{a})^2 = 5,b = \sqrt[3]{-125}\).
(1) 如图 1,连接AC,交x轴于点D.
①求点D的坐标;
②在x轴上有一点E,且S_{\triangle ACE} = S_{\triangle ABC},求点E的坐标;
(2) 如图 2,若点F(m,n)是y轴右侧一点,且S_{\triangle FBC} = 20.求7n - 3m的值.

QuestionEN:
In the plane rectangular coordinate system, points \( A(0,a) \), \( B(0,b) \), and \( C(7,-2) \) are given, with \( BC \) connected, \( (\sqrt{a})^2 = 5 \), and \( b = \sqrt[3]{-125} \).  
(1) As shown in Figure 1, connect \( AC \), intersecting the \( x \)-axis at point \( D \).  
① Find the coordinates of point \( D \);  
② There is a point \( E \) on the \( x \)-axis such that \( S_{\triangle ACE} = S_{\triangle ABC} \). Find the coordinates of point \( E \);  
(2) As shown in Figure 2, if point \( F(m,n) \) lies to the right of the \( y \)-axis and \( S_{\triangle FBC} = 20 \), find the value of \( 7n - 3m \).

