QuestionCN:
如图,一次函数y=kx+n的图象经过点A(a,3)和点B(b,-6),与x轴交于点C,反比例函数y=m/x的图象经过点A和点B,连接OA,已知sin∠AOC=3/5.
(1)求反比例函数和直线AB的表达式;
(2)点Q(0,t)为y轴上一动点,且∠AQB为钝角,求点Q的纵坐标t的取值范围;
(3)点D在直线AB上且在第二象限反比例函数图象的上方运动,过点D作x轴、y轴的垂线分别交反比例函数的图像于点F、E,直线EF分别交x轴、y轴于点N、M,设点D的横坐标为s,求OM/ONー3/s的值.

QuestionEN:
As shown in the figure, the graph of the linear function \( y = kx + n \) passes through points \( A(a, 3) \) and \( B(b, -6) \), intersecting the x-axis at point \( C \). The graph of the inverse proportional function \( y = \frac{m}{x} \) passes through points \( A \) and \( B \). Connect \( OA \), and it is given that \( \sin \angle AOC = \frac{3}{5} \).  

(1) Find the expressions for the inverse proportional function and the line \( AB \);  
(2) Point \( Q(0, t) \) is a moving point on the y-axis, and \( \angle AQB \) is an obtuse angle. Determine the range of the y-coordinate \( t \) for point \( Q \);  
(3) Point \( D \) moves on the line \( AB \) in the second quadrant above the graph of the inverse proportional function. Perpendicular lines are drawn from \( D \) to the x-axis and y-axis, intersecting the graph of the inverse proportional function at points \( F \) and \( E \), respectively. The line \( EF \) intersects the x-axis and y-axis at points \( N \) and \( M \). Given the x-coordinate of \( D \) as \( s \), find the value of \( \frac{OM}{ON} - \frac{3}{s} \).

AnswerEN:
(1) The inverse proportional function is given by \(y=-\frac{12}{x}\), and the linear function AB is given by \(y=-\frac{3}{2}x-3\);  
(2) The range of the vertical coordinate \(t\) of point Q is \(\frac{-\sqrt{113}-3}{2}<t<\frac{\sqrt{113}-3}{2}\), and \(t\neq-3\);  
(3) The value of \(\frac{OM}{ON}-\frac{3}{s}\) is \(\frac{3}{2}\).

